Linux Hardeningn Semi Automatic Bash Script.

-- SSH Hardening 
-- Firewall Hardening  | Iptable Rules 
-- Log management     
-- antimalware 

Installing tools 

- lynis
- ansible
- dev-sec.io playbook
- rkhunter   | malware scanner
- apt-lischanges
- sysstat | systemc accounting tools
- fail2ban | intrusion prevention
- aide | file integrity tools
- unattended-upgrades | automatic update
- auditd | log management  , aureport 
- snort | IDPS  # optional 



## with this Hardening script the lynis Hardening score is on an average 80% achievable 